snippet.title: JUMANJI: WILD ADVENTURES - GAMEPLAY TRAILER
snippet.description:
The hostile and uncharted world of JUMANJI will never fail to test you. Tackle fiendish puzzles to get to the lost treasure. Courageously face deadly foes, fierce predators, and devious traps 👹. Then survive hazardous terrain, like the sweltering jungle and fetid swamps 😓, to find The Jaguar's Eye and make it home in JUMANJI: Wild Adventures 🎮. Out Nov 3! #JUMANJIWildAdventures #JUMANJI
